   "source": [
    "**8.2 Hypothesis Formulation:  \n",
    "Hypothesis 2: Average time between orders:  \n",
    "H0: The average time between orders of mobile users is equal to the average for stationary users.  \n",
    "H1: The average time between orders of mobile users is greater than that of stationary users.**"
   ]
